Alberta Vaughn https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Alberta_Vaughn 0 Alberta Vaughn (June 27, 1904 – April 26, 1992) was an American actress in silent motion pictures and early Western sound films. She appeared in some 130 motion pictures. She died in California at age 87.
